147
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:56,400
But since I met you,

148
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,940
three years after my family's downfall,

149
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,680
I finally feel that

150
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,320
I have a soul again.

151
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:08,720
You truly are my future husband.

152
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,560
It's alright.

153
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:17,600
I'll try my best to fight those bad people with you.

154
