You should rest first.

433
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:12,840
Rest a bit.

434
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:16,680
I, Zhang Guicai,

435
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:18,880
became an imperial secret agent at 14

436
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:20,640
