437
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:21,360
Today,

438
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:24,880
I can finally serve my country openly.

439
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:32,240
To conceal my identity before,

440
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:34,440
I always pretended to be old and feeble.

441
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:37,400
Until Brother Xu started investigating the accounts,

442
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:39,440
I finally resumed my martial arts training.

443
00:26:39,440 --> 00:26:41,400
Today, let me show you all

444
00:26:41,520 --> 00:26:44,720
