Surprisingly.

567
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:30,760
He actually opened a restaurant

568
00:31:30,840 --> 00:31:32,480
called Lihen Tower.

569
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,680
He brews his own wine every day.

570
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:35,440
He says

571
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:37,000
he hopes everyone who comes to drink at Lihen Tower

572
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:38,400
can drown their sorrows.

573
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:39,120
So.

574
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:40,240
we now have a place

575
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:41,680
where we can always get free food and drinks,

576
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:42,680
and this is it.

577
00:31:43,360 --> 00:31:44,200
Very nice.

578
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:45,370
You're here.

579
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:47,840
Congratulations, Fang.

580
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:49,600
Congratulations, Young Master Fang.

581
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:50,240
Ali,

582
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:53,000
your Lihen Tower is getting more and more famous.

583
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:55,200
Soon all of Chang'an will know about it.

584
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:57,680
As expected from the former head of the merchants' guild,

585
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:59,000
your work is exceptional.

586
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,000
It's hard to please everyone.

587
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:01,200
I still have much to improve.

588
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,280
Come in, please.

589
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:03,840
Let's go.

590
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:07,440
Erha.

591
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:08,920
Here's the menu.

592
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:09,440
Coming.

593
00:32:17,520 --> 00:32:19,380
As usual, I'll order everything.

594
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,680
You order everything every time.

595
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:23,400
I really don't understand why you still look at the menu.

596
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:25,200
You never pay when you come to eat here.

597
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:28,260
My parents will go broke because of you sooner or later.

598
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:30,440
You all go upstairs and wait.

599
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:31,960
The dishes will be brought up soon.

600
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:33,520
I'll prepare the fish today.

601
00:32:33,520 --> 00:32:34,200
Brother Xu.

602
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:35,440
I'll help you then.

603
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:35,960
Great.

604
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:36,760
Oh, right.

605
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:39,600
Last time you said fish tastes better with sugar.

606
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:40,460
Add more sugar.

607
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:42,920
Xiaofei, you can't cook at all.

608
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,200
Stop talking nonsense.

609
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:45,400
Just leave it to Ziqi.

610
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,170
Let's go.

611
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:47,920
Okay.

612
00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:49,080
I'll go first.

613
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:49,640
Come.

614
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:52,240
Let's go upstairs first.

615
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,160
Fang Lihen.

616
00:33:02,840 --> 00:33:04,480
I suddenly feel that

617
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:07,120
your attitude toward me seems different now.

618
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:09,440
We're old friends.

619
00:33:09,440 --> 00:33:10,840
What could be different?

620
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:15,160
It's just a bit subtle.

621
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:18,240
And the way you look at me now

622
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:19,440
is much calmer.

623
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:21,040
Is it?

624
00:33:22,520 --> 00:33:23,720
Maybe before I was

625
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:25,970
too obsessed with everything.

626
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:27,800
I always felt I had no choice.

627
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,440
With the chamber of commerce,

628
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,440
with family matters,

629
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,170
and with you,

630
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:32,600
I was too fixated.

631
00:33:32,600 --> 00:33:34,400
I cared too much about gains and losses,

632
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,920
worried too much about outcomes,

633
00:33:35,920 --> 00:33:38,050
and all my feelings became distorted.

634
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,720
Who told you to pick the wrong name?

635
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:43,480
'Hatred' all day long.

636
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,440
My father named me Lihen

637
00:33:46,480 --> 00:33:49,340
hoping I would stay away from obsession and hatred.

638
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:54,120
Xiaofei, thank you for your passion and courage

639
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:55,920
for showing me

640
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:57,400
that blind obsession

641
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:59,180
isn't always a good thing.

642
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:03,840
Life actually offers many choices.

643
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,440
Alright.

644
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:07,680
Enough talk.

645
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:09,840
Hurry upstairs and get ready.

646
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:10,360
The food will be here soon.

647
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:10,960
Okay.

648
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:31,239
Drink to forget sorrows.

649
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:42,280
Yes.

650
00:34:43,159 --> 00:34:44,560
Drink to forget sorrows,

651
00:34:44,639 --> 00:34:46,040
and the world feels vast.

652
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:49,080
Lihen Tower.

653
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:50,840
Drink to forget sorrows.

654
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:53,400
It seems you're a man with a story.

655
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:56,719
I am

656
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,120
Fang Lihen.

657
00:34:59,720 --> 00:35:00,840
I am Qingshang.

658
00:35:01,080 --> 00:35:02,400
I just arrived in Chang'an

659
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,560
and opened a music shop

660
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:05,400
next to your establishment.

661
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:08,040
I know a little about music and literature.

662
00:35:09,240 --> 00:35:11,440
Miss Qingshang, you are quite refined.

663
00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:13,800
Life is short,

664
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:16,240
that's why we need wine and song.

665
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:19,160
It seems you also have a story to tell.

666
00:35:21,240 --> 00:35:22,240
May I

667
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:25,400
invite you for a drink?

668
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:30,640
Very well. Drink to forget sorrows.

669
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:32,240
Please.

670
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:38,040
Hello.

671
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:41,400
I'm the master's attendant.

672
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,260
My name is Erha.

673
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:43,960
I'm my lady's maid.

674
00:35:43,960 --> 00:35:44,820
My name is Samo.

675
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,520
Samo.

676
00:35:46,640 --> 00:35:47,440
Samo...

677
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:48,780
What a lovely name.

678
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:50,440
Erha.

679
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:51,800
How festive.

680
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,080
As for me,

681
00:36:05,640 --> 00:36:07,720
thanks to my clever business mind,

682
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:10,320
I've officially become the Chamber of Commerce president.

683
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,640
As for Xu Ziqi,

684
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:14,080
he finally managed to retire early

685
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:16,440
and contentedly became a house husband,

686
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:19,820
enjoying the blissful life of being kept by a wealthy wife.

687
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:22,720
However, he made an agreement with the Empress

688
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,800
that if the Great Tang ever faces any danger,

689
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:26,660
he, as Tang's top imperial agent,

690
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:28,680
must be the first to take action.

691
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:32,480
Good.

692
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,480
Finally, everything is settled.

693
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:37,080
Everything's back on track.

694
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:39,570
We should start planning our wedding now.

695
00:36:45,040 --> 00:36:46,700
Making clothes for one couple

696
00:36:47,160 --> 00:36:48,420
is exhausting enough,

697
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:50,900
and now I have to make them for you two as well.

698
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:57,240
But making clothes just for my darling

699
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:59,440
is worth any effort.

700
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:04,440
It's just too much work.

701
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:08,560
My body is so tired.

702
00:37:08,640 --> 00:37:09,560
Are you sick?

703
00:37:09,560 --> 00:37:10,760
Do you have medicine?

704
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:25,720
No way.

705
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,360
Oh, it's you.

706
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:37,640
Welcome the bride!

707
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,320
Congratulations, Mr. Xu.

708
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:12,180
Congratulations, Miss Xiaofei.

709
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:15,400
Congratulations, Boss Xu! Best wishes!

710
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:17,260
We've finally made it to this day.

711
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:19,280
Have a little Xiaoqi soon!

712
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,440
Bride, stop here.

713
00:38:37,560 --> 00:38:38,960
Step over the fire basin.

714
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:41,920
Be dignified in behavior and gentle in manner.

715
00:38:42,040 --> 00:38:45,370
Husband leads, wife follows, prosperity comes with unity.

716
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:47,900
Cherish your peers and respect your elders.

717
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:53,400
Good.

718
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,580
First bow to heaven and earth.

719
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,720
Second bow to the parents.

720
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,410
Husband and wife bow to each other.

721
00:39:33,040 --> 00:39:33,400
Wonderful.

722
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:33,960
Good.

723
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:37,440
The ceremony is complete.

724
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,240
Wait a moment.

725
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:42,090
I want to add one more thing.

726
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:46,080
Now the groom may kiss the bride.

727
00:39:51,160 --> 00:39:52,960
Children shouldn't watch this.

728
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:11,960
Escort to the bridal chamber.

729
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:13,720
Alright.

730
00:40:45,560 --> 00:40:46,280
Well...

731
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:48,400
I have no experience.

732
00:40:48,720 --> 00:40:51,960
I don't have much experience either.

733
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,920
Then I ask you, wife,

734
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:57,840
to work with me.

735
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:00,930
Then I ask you, husband,

736
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:02,880
to be gentle.

737
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,170
Don't panic.

738
00:41:11,240 --> 00:41:12,560
No rush.

739
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:13,640
Keep your hands steady.

740
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:14,720
Not shaking.

741
00:41:34,720 --> 00:41:35,520
Who pushed me?

742
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:39,160
What are you doing in here?

743
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:41,040
Can you all please quiet down?

744
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:42,120
Um...

745
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:58,120
We're

746
00:41:59,600 --> 00:42:00,840
feeling a bit hot.

747
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:01,400
Yes, indeed.

748
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:02,160
Why don't we

749
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:03,980
have hot pot together?

750
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:06,600
H-hot pot?

751
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:07,120
Hot pot.

752
00:42:07,560 --> 00:42:09,240
So hot.

753
00:42:12,160 --> 00:42:13,960
Hot pot sounds good.

754
00:42:13,960 --> 00:42:14,890
Hot pot is great.

755
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:20,480
Great.

756
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:21,000
Yes.

757
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:21,560
Good.

758
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:22,640
Alright.

759
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:23,660
Excellent.

760
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:32,360
Cheers!

761
00:42:40,240 --> 00:42:40,800
Xiaofei,

762
00:42:42,440 --> 00:42:44,960
do you have any unfulfilled dreams?

763
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:47,960
Good question. Let me think.

764
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:51,920
What about you all? What are your dreams?

765
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:55,920
I just want to marry Jin'er as soon as possible,

766
00:42:56,120 --> 00:42:57,380
the sooner the better.

767
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,530
I hope our business becomes more successful,

768
00:43:01,560 --> 00:43:03,560
so everyone knows that I, Gu Jin'er,

769
00:43:03,600 --> 00:43:05,160
even without being a courtesan,

770
00:43:05,160 --> 00:43:06,960
can still live a wonderful life.

771
00:43:08,400 --> 00:43:11,000
I hope all men in the world can be themselves,

772
00:43:11,520 --> 00:43:13,920
without worrying about others' opinions.

773
00:43:14,520 --> 00:43:15,320
Well said.

774
00:43:15,480 --> 00:43:16,280
As for me,

775
00:43:16,440 --> 00:43:18,160
I hope all women in the world

776
00:43:18,240 --> 00:43:19,920
can bravely be themselves.

777
00:43:20,520 --> 00:43:22,920
I want to be the first female scholar in the Tang Dynasty,

778
00:43:22,920 --> 00:43:24,600
a female scholar who can

779
00:43:24,600 --> 00:43:26,320
advocate for all women's welfare.

780
00:43:26,320 --> 00:43:29,250
I hope everyone can have close friends by their side,

781
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:31,440
family and loved ones to rely on.

782
00:43:32,480 --> 00:43:33,960
May everyone's life be stable,

783
00:43:33,960 --> 00:43:35,560
and their families blessed.

784
00:43:38,960 --> 00:43:41,880
I hope there will be no more wars in this world,

785
00:43:42,240 --> 00:43:42,970
and Anpingle

786
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:45,320
will no longer need to house anyone.

787
00:43:45,760 --> 00:43:46,690
If that happens,

788
00:43:47,640 --> 00:43:49,370
wouldn't the world be at peace?

789
00:43:50,720 --> 00:43:53,880
I hope not to disappoint my ancestors' efforts,

790
00:43:54,040 --> 00:43:58,000
and become a wealthy person who serves the country and its people.

791
00:43:59,240 --> 00:43:59,760
Good.

792
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:00,480
Well said.

793
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:03,480
To our hopes!

794
00:44:03,640 --> 00:44:05,440
Cheers!
